Have you received *<%= @donation.book %>* yet? <%= @donation.donor.name %> agreed to send you this book on <%= l @granted_at.to_date, format: :short %> (<%= distance_of_time_in_words_to_now @granted_at %> ago), but we have not yet confirmed that they have sent it.

If you *have* received it, let us know using this link:

<%= edit_donation_status_url(@donation, status: "received") %>

If you have *not* received it, you can try to find another donor using this link:

<%= cancel_donation_url(@donation, reason: "not_received") %>
